{"tid":500342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年立法會，我票都唔會去投#bye#","createTime":"2017-12-15T16:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T01:57:21.000Z","uid":14918,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"910b7c9a205a2e962f0e76756f0ac948317f1b3e","tid":500342,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"唔會投一班政治潔癖，偶像包袱既泛民 <br />\n唔會索性投建制 <br />\n<br />\n只會連票都唔投<br />\n<br />\n希望全世界杯葛立法會<br />\n最低投票率 議會一黨獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由得立法機關死亡仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港市民主動放棄立法權<br />\n三權不再分立 政治上搞臭香港仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其"},{"pid":"1a4fdb0fbaa2f544292efe9b05e3786adff9b622","tid":500342,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"主動放棄立法權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要求政府官員成為立法會既當然議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528a49ba4217bc7dbc821cd141dbc99c50bdcb15","tid":500342,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主動放棄立法權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要求政府官員成為立法會既當然議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n林鄭話政府唔會做有害市民利益既事<br />\n<br />\n咁官員做埋當然議員仲無問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c